name: E-DRA EK300 KATANA
description: E-DRA EK300 KATANA is a gaming keyboard with a compact and ergonomic design. It features 104 keys with RGB lighting, providing a vibrant and customizable gaming experience. The keyboard also includes a detachable wrist rest for added comfort during long gaming sessions.

name: E-DRA EK396
description: The E-DRA EK396 is a mechanical gaming keyboard designed for gamers who demand high-performance and customizable options. It features a compact layout with a 96-key design, allowing for a more efficient and ergonomic typing experience. The keyboard is built with hot-swappable switches, which means you can easily swap out switches without needing any special tools.

name: E-DRA EK314W
description: E-DRA EK314W is a keyboard designed for gaming and typing. It features a white LED backlight that can be customized in different colors and modes. The keyboard is made of durable ABS material and has a compact layout with 87 keys. It uses blue mechanical switches that provide tactile feedback and audible click sound. The keyboard also has multimedia function keys and a Windows key lock function to prevent accidental presses. It connects to the computer via USB and is compatible with Windows and Mac operating systems.

name: E-DRA EK368L - Beta
description: The E-DRA EK368L - Beta is a gaming keyboard designed for gamers who prioritize responsiveness and durability. It features blue mechanical switches, which are known for their tactile feedback and audible click sound, as well as full anti-ghosting and N-key rollover, ensuring accurate and precise keystrokes even during intense gaming sessions. The keyboard also includes customizable RGB lighting, allowing users to create a personalized look to match their setup. The EK368L is built with a durable aluminum frame and includes a detachable wrist rest for added comfort during long gaming sessions.

name: E-DRA EK384Wv2
description: The E-DRA EK384Wv2 is a wireless mechanical gaming keyboard designed for gamers and typists. It features a compact 84-key layout with white LED backlighting, which can be adjusted or turned off to suit your preferences. The keyboard uses Gateron mechanical switches, which provide tactile feedback and durability. It also has anti-ghosting technology to ensure accurate input, and full-key rollover for fast and responsive gaming.

name: E-DRA EK3104 - RGB - Blood Warrior
description: The E-DRA EK3104 RGB Blood Warrior is a gaming keyboard designed for gamers who want a combination of style and performance. It features RGB backlighting that can be customized to suit the user's preferences, as well as a durable construction that can withstand heavy use. The keyboard also includes anti-ghosting and N-key rollover features to ensure that all key presses are registered accurately, even during fast-paced gaming sessions. Other features of the E-DRA EK3104 include multimedia controls, a detachable wrist rest, and a braided USB cable for enhanced durability.

name: E-DRA EM6102 Pro
description: E-DRA EM6102 Pro is a gaming mouse with features such as high-precision optical sensor, adjustable DPI (up to 7200), programmable buttons, and customizable RGB lighting. It also has a comfortable ergonomic design for long gaming sessions and comes with software for further customization.

name: E-DRA EM601v2
description: E-DRA EM601v2 is a gaming mouse designed for gamers with a high level of accuracy and responsiveness. It features an ergonomic design with a comfortable grip, a high-quality optical sensor with a sensitivity of up to 6400 DPI, and six programmable buttons that can be customized to suit your gaming needs. The mouse also comes with RGB lighting that adds a stylish touch to your gaming setup, and it supports various operating systems including Windows, macOS, and Linux. With its high-performance features, the E-DRA EM601v2 gaming mouse is a great choice for serious gamers who demand precision and reliability.

name: E-DRA EM624
description: E-DRA EM624 is a gaming mouse designed for gamers with a sleek and ergonomic design. It features 6 programmable buttons, an adjustable DPI range of up to 7200, and a customizable RGB lighting system. The mouse also has a braided cable for durability and accuracy, and comes with a software that allows for customization of macros and button functions.

name: Logitech Pro Gen 2
description: The Logitech Pro X Wireless Lightspeed Gaming Headset (also known as the Logitech Pro Gen 2) is a high-end wireless gaming headset designed for gamers who demand top-tier audio quality and performance. It features advanced Pro-G 50mm drivers for crisp, detailed sound, DTS Headphone:X 2.0 surround sound for immersive gaming experiences, and a high-performance ClearCast noise-canceling microphone for clear communication with teammates.

name: Logitech G733 Lightspeed
description: Logitech G733 Lightspeed is a wireless gaming headset designed for PC gaming. It features Lightspeed wireless technology, which offers a low-latency connection with a range of up to 20 meters. The headset also comes with DTS Headphone:X 2.0 surround sound, which provides a more immersive gaming experience. The G733 Lightspeed has a lightweight and comfortable design, with adjustable RGB lighting on the ear cups. It also comes with a detachable microphone that has a noise-canceling feature for clearer voice communication.

name: Logitech Z213 2.1
description: The Logitech Z213 2.1 is a speaker system that includes two satellite speakers and a subwoofer. The system has a total output power of 7 watts RMS, with 2.5 watts per satellite speaker and 2 watts for the subwoofer. The satellite speakers have a compact design and can be placed on a desk or mounted on the wall. The subwoofer is compact as well and can be placed under a desk or in a corner. The system includes a wired control pod that allows you to adjust the volume and turn the system on and off. It also includes a headphone jack and an auxiliary input for connecting other devices. The Logitech Z213 2.1 is compatible with Windows and Mac computers, as well as other audio devices that have a 3.5mm output.

name: Razer Seiren V2
description: The Razer Seiren V2 X is a USB condenser microphone designed for professional-grade streaming and audio recording. It features a cardioid pickup pattern to capture sound sources directly in front of the mic, and has a built-in shock mount to reduce vibrations and handling noise. The microphone also has a zero-latency headphone monitoring port, allowing you to hear your voice in real time without any delay. It has a frequency response of 20Hz-20kHz, and comes with a removable desk stand and a mic adapter.

name: HyperX DuoCast RGB
description: The HyperX DuoCast RGB is a gaming microphone with dual condenser capsules for clear audio recording. It features a built-in shock mount to reduce vibration and noise, and has a cardioid pickup pattern to focus on the user's voice while minimizing background noise. The microphone also includes customizable RGB lighting to add a stylish touch to your setup. It connects via USB and is compatible with PC, PS4, and Mac.

name: Asus ROG THETA 7.1
description: The Asus ROG Theta 7.1 is a gaming headset with 7.1 surround sound technology. It features four high-quality Ess Sabre DACs and a built-in amplifier that delivers powerful and immersive audio. The headset is also equipped with an AI noise-cancelling microphone that filters out background noise for clear communication with teammates. The Asus ROG Theta 7.1 has customizable RGB lighting and is compatible with a wide range of devices, including PC, Mac, and gaming consoles.

name: Logitech G560 LIGHTSYNC RGB
description: The Logitech G560 LIGHTSYNC RGB is a gaming speaker system that features dynamic and immersive RGB lighting synced to in-game action and audio. The system includes two satellite speakers and a powerful subwoofer for clear, crisp sound quality with deep bass. It also has built-in DTS:X Ultra surround sound, allowing you to pinpoint enemy positions and immerse yourself in your favorite games. The speakers are compatible with multiple devices, including PCs, gaming consoles, and smartphones, and can be controlled through the Logitech G HUB software. The G560 is a great addition to any gaming setup, enhancing both your audio and visual experience.
